Depends: libtelepathy-glib0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: GLib Telepathy connection manager library (debug symbols)
 This package contains support for debugging programs that use telepathy-glib,
 a GLib-based library for Telepathy connection managers.
 .
 Telepathy is a D-Bus framework for unifying real time communication,
 including instant messaging, voice calls and video calls. It abstracts
